snippet: The proposed legislation would require a warning on the front of all beverage containers with added sweeteners that have 75 or more calories in every 12 ounces.
lead_paragraph: The proposed legislation would require a warning on the front of all beverage containers with added sweeteners that have 75 or more calories in every 12 ounces.
